params.name: text_config
params.description: Dictionary of configuration options used to initialize Owlv2TextConfig.

params.name: vision_config
params.description: Dictionary of configuration options used to initialize Owlv2VisionConfig.

params.name: projection_dim
params.description: Dimensionality of text and vision projection layers.

params.name: logit_scale_init_value
params.description: The initial value of the logit_scale parameter. Default is used as per the original OWLv2implementation.

params.name: return_dict
params.description: Whether or not the model should return a dictionary. If False, returns a tuple.
